{"tid":2156066,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Google證實不再直接應港府要求提供用戶數據","createTime":"2020-08-14T07:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T10:04:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"210514d0bef70d653de581b63de80dc053592336","tid":2156066,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:54:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543724-20200814.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543724-20200814.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcZa4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=1b1aa0f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543724-20200814.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=915dda51\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543724-20200814.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國大型科技公司Google證實，在中國實施《港區國安法》之後，將不會再直接應香港當局要求，提供用戶的數據。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle發表聲明，指自從新法例在6月生效後，公司從未向香港當局提供任何數據，此後亦不會再直接回應這類要求，指美國以外的機構，可以透過外交程序，尋求以供刑事調查之用的數據資料。Google又指，公司會拒絕範圍太廣的數據請求，以保障用戶私隱。<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》報道，Google星期四通知香港警方，指當局需要透過美國的《司法互助條約》提出任何數據請求。報道指，有關過程繁瑣，而且要由美國司法部處理，可能需時數星期甚至數個月，安排等同將香港當成中國內地來處理。<br />\n<br />\n除了Google，Facebook及Twitter在上月先後宣布，暫停處理香港政府對索取用戶數據的申請。"},{"pid":"7b2abf80d74c7be232692c8ec84cc3f0fba3aa16","tid":2156066,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:55:53.000Z","msg":"反而想知之前係點提供,出信就畀資料？"},{"pid":"4a8eca1e0fbf0ef3e59064f663feec10e42a4d01","tid":2156066,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b2abf80d74c7be232692c8ec84cc3f0fba3aa16","tid":2156066,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:55:53.000Z","msg":"反而想知之前係點提供,出信就畀資料？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"通常都係既"},{"pid":"4f3ae1d04fa6becb83d9afbd65faf1ff7b1fc678","tid":2156066,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote